  "comment": "Followbot 1500 LED is powered by a high-output 1500W LED light engine, delivering intense brightness ideal for long throws of 200 feet or more. Designed as a manually operated followspot, it features manual zoom and focus for precise beam control.\n\nTwo rotary knobs provide hands-on adjustment of the motorized frost and beam softener, while a side control panel allows accurate dimming or dousing. When connected via DMX, operators can remotely control intensity, strobe, and blackout functions from any DMX controller. A built-in gobo and color filter slot supports custom color filters or high-temperature gobos for striking projection effects.\n\nThe front bezel accommodates an optional color carousel for expanded creative flexibility. The Followbot 1500 LED ships complete with a heavy-duty tripod and protective flight case, making it a powerful and tour-ready solution for professional applications.",
